Yeah buddy! Its finally out!
Welcome to JACKS Multigames, it is ages ago since I started the map but alot of people
forced me to do the map! Thanks to all of them. I spend alot of time to it and i hope all of you like it.

The Gameplay


Well, this Multigames contains alot of variation with 15 Minigames and Randomspawns.
The 15 Minigames are:
  • Awp
  • Breakwall
  • Simon Says
  • Mp5 & Deagle
  • Build Wars aka Castle War
  • Long Jump
  • Bunny Hop
  • Race
  • Iceskate
  • Musical Doors
  • Climb
  • Zombie Massacre
  • Las0rs
  • Tetris
  • Slidekill

    • Features


  • Good Musics
  • 56 Spawns(I think)
  • Custom Material
  • and many more>
